msgid ""
"ON時: 画像ごとに vmin/vmax を自動計算。\n"
"  vmin = 画像最小値 を切り下げ\n"
"  vmax = 画像最大値 + 1 を切り上げ\n"
"OFF時: 入力欄の vmin / vmax を固定使用。"
msgstr ""
"When ON: automatically calculate vmin/vmax for each image.\n"
"  vmin = round down the image minimum\n"
"  vmax = round up the image maximum + 1\n"
"When OFF: use the fixed vmin / vmax values from the input fields."

#: guis/GUI02_PlotProfiler.py:771
msgid "線幅（ピクセル）:"
msgstr "Line Width (pixels):"

#: guis/GUI02_PlotProfiler.py:774
msgid ""
"高さプロファイルを取得する線分の垂直方向の幅（ピクセル数）。\n"
"1 にすると線分の真上のみ、3 以上にすると周囲数ピクセルも含めて\n"
"下の「計算方法」で集計した値が高さとして使われます。\n"
"ナノファイバーの場合、3〜5 程度に設定するとノイズの影響を抑えられます。"
msgstr ""
"Width perpendicular to the line segment used to obtain the height profile"
" (pixels).\n"
"If set to 1, only the pixels directly on the line are used. If set to 3 "
"or higher,\n"
"nearby pixels are also included, and the value aggregated by the "
"\"Calculation Method\" below is used as the height.\n"
"For nanofibers, setting this to about 3-5 can reduce the effect of noise."

#: guis/GUI02_PlotProfiler.py:792
msgid "計算方法"
msgstr "Calculation Method"

#: guis/GUI02_PlotProfiler.py:795
msgid ""
"上の「線幅」が 2 以上のとき、線分垂直方向の複数ピクセルから\n"
"1 つの高さ値を決める集計方法。\n"
"「最大」: 最も高い値を採用（ファイバー本体の高さを拾いやすい）\n"
"「最小」: 最も低い値を採用（背景レベルの確認に有用）\n"
"「平均」: 平均値を採用（ノイズを平滑化したいとき）"
msgstr ""
"Aggregation method used to determine one height value from multiple "
"pixels perpendicular to the line segment when \"Line Width\" above is 2 "
"or higher.\n"
"\"Maximum\": use the highest value (easier to capture the fiber body "
"height)\n"
"\"Minimum\": use the lowest value (useful for checking the background "
"level)\n"
"\"Average\": use the mean value (when you want to smooth noise)"

